one upon a time there was a crow who was very thirsty due to lot of heat. it was a season of summer. the thirsty crow was looking for water . on his way he found a jar filled with water and came down and tried to drink the water but he was unable because his beak was not allowing him to peak inside and drink water. he found a solution he went to find some stones nearby him he collected many stones . after he finished collecting stones she started putting the stones in the water and the water level rised up and he was able to drink water .
